      <title>萬科稱已製定應對短期流動性壓力的計劃</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[國有房地產開發商萬科表示，該公司面臨短期流動性壓力和經營困難，但補充稱，該公司已準備好「一籃子計畫」來穩定業務並削減債務。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:37:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
